         <abstract id="aspace_e65f9fe4096e8d40932a2c5e5d4f519d">Collection consists of 16mm motion picture film <emph render="italic">Colossal Keepsake</emph> which documents the creation and gifting to Yale University of "Lipstick (Ascending) on Caterpillar Tracks" sculpture by Claes Oldenburg.  The film was shot in 1969 by Peter Hentschel and William Richardson, graduate students at the Yale School of Architecture.</abstract>
